Class ValueAliasProcessorGroupFactoryBean

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Administrable, org.springframework.beans.factory.FactoryBean, IComponent
public class ValueAliasProcessorGroupFactoryBean
extends AbstractSimpleRecordProcessorGroupFactoryBean

FactoryBean that mimics an old style ValueAliasPipe. The Factory generates a ProcessorGroup of ConditionProcessors. Each procesor is initialised using the attribute and one key/value pair from the aliasmap. Each key in the map defines an expression that evaluates to a SimpleRecord attribute value to alias and each value from the key/value pair is an expression that evaluates to a new value for that same attribute.

Properties 

 attribute        Attribute whose value is being aliased
 aliasMap         Map of old to new values. Keys and Values are both expressions.
